title: The Lambo problem
body:
The legendary Queen Frog, champion of the League of Valets, has found herself in a perilous situation. Your help is needed to decide the fates of several lives.

Queen Frog is about to drive an out-of-control green Lambo into a group of shaken Firestarters. The mysterious Firestarters are essential to the ecosystem, for they provide the flames upon which staking can take place. 

Her only options are to stay on course, speeding towards the group, or to swerve right into the wilderness.

Oh, and did we mention there's an unsuspecting Stowaway in the trunk?

![Decision](https://carbonswap.exchange/static/media/lamboproblem.f034708c.jpg)

To see how Queen Frog got here, read over the full story at 
[CarbonSwap](https://carbonswap.exchange/#/welcome).

So?..
